title: 4Leaf eSports Trials Close at 1pm AEDT!
body:
Hey guys just letting you know that I will be not taking any more trialers after 1PM AEDT, There has been a way bigger turnout then I expected with seeing over 40 expressions of interest.

So if you would like to still have a go at trialling add me in game - CCG Dunbt, make sure you're Platinum or higher!

Cheers

Brad

EDIT - Trials are now closed!
